{"data":[{"date":"09:14 26/06","title":"HLV Nigeria l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/hlv-nigeria-len-tieng-de-doa-argentina.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 64 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chung k\u1ebft b\u1ea3ng D gi\u1eefa Nigeria v\u00e0 Argentina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArgentina d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, sau \u0111\u00f3 Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thua s\u1ed1c 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/HLV-Gernot-Rohr-noi-ve-tran-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Nigeria vs Argentina \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea5t may cho Argentina l\u00e0 Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Theo \u0111\u00f3 \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Iceland \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng D l\u00fac n\u00e0y ngo\u00e0i Croatia th\u00ec 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f2n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Croatia \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Nigeria x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n Argentina v\u00e0 Iceland m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i nay, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nigeria-vs-argentina-1h00-ngay-276-vua-da-bong-vua-cau-nguyen-421-189578.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nigeria vs Argentina</span> trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u00ec c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Nigeria gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Croatia v\u00e0 Iceland. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu Argentina gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Nigeria \u0111e d\u1ecda Argentina</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 64 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gernot Rohr phat bieu ve tran Nigeria vs Iceland\" title=\"Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/hlv-nigeria-hay-mang-argentina-den-day.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Argentina. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, n\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m 2017 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina 4-2, Nigeria t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Nigeria s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"598","checkdouble":"189586"},{"date":"09:29 26/06","title":"Marco Reus n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \u0111\u1ea9y Mesut Ozil l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-khi-day-mesut-ozil-len-bang-ghe-du-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marco Reus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Dortmund \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marco Reus \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Mesut Ozil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMesut Ozil \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-1. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb HLV Low tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marco Reus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marco Reus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-khi-day-mesut-ozil-len-bang-ghe-du-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Reus \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Ozil v\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F V\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u00f4ng Low \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Marco Reus \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng thay v\u00ec Mesut Ozil, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup-421-189402.html\" target=\"_blank\">Marco Reus khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t</span>, anh g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Reus ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1, sau \u0111\u00f3 anh ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Toni Kroos ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Dortmund s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay v\u00ec Ozil. Marco Reus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Dortmund \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, anh \u1ea5y v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Low. Ozil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Reus tin \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F. Hi\u1ec7n Mexico \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n x\u1ebfp sau v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Reus va man tro lai tuyet voi\" title=\"Reus v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Reus tin \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Marco Reus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, \u0110\u1ee9c bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"597","checkdouble":"189587"},{"date":"09:18 26/06","title":"HLV Argentina tin Messi s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/hlv-argentina-tin-messi-se-toa-sang-truoc-nigeria.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6 (V\u00f2ng 16 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 266 (V-League 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 266 (V-League 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/truc-tiep-flc-thanh-hoa-vs-hai-phong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nTr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018 gi\u1eefa Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng m\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m 8/6 v\u1eeba qua. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng sau khi thanh l\u00fd m\u1ed9t l\u00fac 3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n L\u1ea1ch Tray.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3, Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. V\u0169 Minh Tu\u1ea5n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, Thanh H\u00f3a c\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e0ng kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a sau 3 tr\u1eadn, Thanh H\u00f3a leo m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean BXH, ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Thanh H\u00f3a hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n khi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean 5 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y - m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t khi ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch. 5 tr\u1eadn xa nh\u00e0 v\u1eeba qua, H\u1ea3i P\u00f2ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang h\u1ed3i sinh \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ra v\u1ec1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nThanh H\u00f3a: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng; \u0110\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ed3ng, V\u0103n Nam, Minh T\u00f9ng, Xu\u00e2n H\u01b0ng, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng, Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecbnh, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00f9ng, Omar.<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: V\u0103n L\u00e2m; Ho\u00e0i D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Schmidt, Ho\u00e0ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Qu\u1ed1c Trung, Anh H\u00f9ng, Ng\u1ecdc T\u00e2n, Th\u00e0nh Long, Stevens, Fagan, \u0110\u00ecnh B\u1ea3o.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"596","checkdouble":"189588"},{"date":"09:55 26/06","title":"MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i \"bom t\u1ea5n\" v\u1edbi PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/mu-san-sang-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-psg.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Verratti</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Carrick gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, Mourinho \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marco Verratti c\u1ee7a PSG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hy sinh Pogba, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hy sinh Pogba, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Hy-sinh-Pogba,-MU-muon-mua-Marco-Verratti-bang-duoc-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Verratti\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Marco Verratti c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 s\u00fat xa.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi PSG, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede H\u00e8 2017, su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa Barca \u0111\u00e3 mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 khi Barca ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 80 tri\u1ec7u euro trong khi PSG \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang khao kh\u00e1t Verratti, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda PSG y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Verratti</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-mua-verratti-voi-gia-75-trieu-bang-172-187639.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Verratti</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU san sang doi Pogba lay Verratti\" title=\"MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y Verratti\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/mu-san-sang-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-psg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y Verratti</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, M.U s\u1ebd g\u1eedi 2 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Pogba v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u00f4ng n\u00e0y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVerratti d\u00f9 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi PSG nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng PSG s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi M.U, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m v\u1edbi Pogba.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"595","checkdouble":"189590"},{"date":"10:22 26/06","title":"Sao Arsenal quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ti\u1ec5n Messi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/sao-arsenal-quyet-tam-tien-messi-ve-nuoc-som.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alex Iwobi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp m\u1edf ra v\u1edbi Nigeria</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018, Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi thua Croatia 0-2. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Iwobi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alex Iwobi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Alex-Iwobi-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nigeria th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 g\u1eb7p Iceland, Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d th\u1eafp l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng D l\u00fac n\u00e0y ngo\u00e0i Croatia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec Nigeria, Argentina v\u00e0 Iceland \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Nigeria s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Argentina, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Nigeria gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-nigeria-len-tieng-de-doa-argentina-421-189586.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina</span>, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 64 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Iwobi c\u0169ng tin Nigeria \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c h\u1ea1 Argentina</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alex Iwobi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Iwobi phat bieu ve tran Nigeria vs Argentina\" title=\"Iwobi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/sao-arsenal-quyet-tam-tien-messi-ve-nuoc-som.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Iwobi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin sau khi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, Nigeria c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina. NHM \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Nigeria v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cArgentina l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, song Nigeria l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"594","checkdouble":"189591"},{"date":"09:48 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/nhan-dinh-thanh-hoa-vs-hai-phong-17h00-ngay-266-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6 (V\u00f2ng 16 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 266 (V-League 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 266 (V-League 2018) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/truc-tiep-flc-thanh-hoa-vs-hai-phong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nTr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018 gi\u1eefa Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng m\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m 8/6 v\u1eeba qua. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng sau khi thanh l\u00fd m\u1ed9t l\u00fac 3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n L\u1ea1ch Tray.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3, Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. V\u0169 Minh Tu\u1ea5n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, Thanh H\u00f3a c\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e0ng kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a sau 3 tr\u1eadn, Thanh H\u00f3a leo m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean BXH, ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Thanh H\u00f3a hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n khi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean 5 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y - m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t khi ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch. 5 tr\u1eadn xa nh\u00e0 v\u1eeba qua, H\u1ea3i P\u00f2ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang h\u1ed3i sinh \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ra v\u1ec1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nThanh H\u00f3a: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng; \u0110\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ed3ng, V\u0103n Nam, Minh T\u00f9ng, Xu\u00e2n H\u01b0ng, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng, Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecbnh, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00f9ng, Omar.<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: V\u0103n L\u00e2m; Ho\u00e0i D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Schmidt, Ho\u00e0ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Qu\u1ed1c Trung, Anh H\u00f9ng, Ng\u1ecdc T\u00e2n, Th\u00e0nh Long, Stevens, Fagan, \u0110\u00ecnh B\u1ea3o.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"593","checkdouble":"189592"},{"date":"11:02 26/06","title":"Chelsea ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/chelsea-hoan-thanh-2-ban-hop-dong-vao-dau-thang-7.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea s\u1eafp b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o ch\u00ed li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba chia tay Napoli c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-hoan-thanh-2-ban-hop-dong-vao-thang-7-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Express, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia, hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecd \u0111ang ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t n\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Conte, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi HLV Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, HLV 58 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea, \u00f4ng h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb The Express c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi, ngay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n mua c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli g\u1eedi l\u00ean BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Daniele Rugani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rugani nhieu kha nang se tro thanh tan binh dau tien cua Arsenal o He 2018\" title=\"Rugani nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/chelsea-hoan-thanh-2-ban-hop-dong-vao-dau-thang-7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rugani nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng Sarri c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Gary Cahill \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n David Luiz l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Daniele Rugani v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi t\u1edbi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang-172-189240.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani</span> th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\u00a0\u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i HLV Sarri c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Morata v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n anh ngay\u00a0H\u00e8 2018. Dries Mertens c\u1ee7a Napoli l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"592","checkdouble":"189593"},{"date":"10:04 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/nhan-dinh-khanh-hoa-vs-binh-duong-17h00-ngay-266-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6 (V\u00f2ng 16 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 266 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 266 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/khanh-hoa-binh-duong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Sanna.KH \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o khi \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean th\u1ee9 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 tr\u00ean BXH. \u1ede v\u00f2ng 15, h\u1ecd su\u00fdt khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC \u00f4m h\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Qu\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u201c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn\u201d. N\u0103m nay, Sanna.KH c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 Zarour v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Toure ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ed7 d\u1ef1a l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 - ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. B.BD kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m n\u00ean v\u1edbi d\u00e0n qu\u00e2n tr\u1ebb n\u00ean th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Sanna.KH.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00e1ch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a HLV Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa hai s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t gi\u00e0, m\u1ed9t tr\u1ebb l\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c -Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1. B.BD kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i m\u01b0\u1edbt m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i. Sanna.KH c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef3 l\u1ee3m v\u00e0 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd trong ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c NHM \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua B.BD v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sau khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 Bi\u1ec3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nSanna.KH: Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh, T\u1ea5n \u0110i\u1ec1n, Ho\u00e0i An, Zarour, Duy Thanh, Nh\u1eadt Nam, Tr\u1ecdng B\u00ecnh, Tr\u00f9m T\u1ec9nh, Ti Ph\u00f4ng, Qu\u1ed1c Ch\u00ed, Toure.<br>\r\nB.BD: T\u1ea5n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Xu\u00e2n Lu\u00e2n, H\u1ed3 T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Ng\u1ecdc M\u1ea1nh, Thanh Long, Hu\u1ef3nh Ph\u00fa, L\u00ea T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Ho\u00e0ng Max, Ti\u1ebfn Linh, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Romario.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"591","checkdouble":"189594"},{"date":"10:53 26/06","title":"T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Morocco: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng nh\u00e0 vua","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/tay-ban-nha-22-marocco-dau-roi-bong-dang-nha-vua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam kh\u00f3 qu\u00ean t\u1ea1i Kaliningrad, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t Morocco \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t La Roja h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o tr\u1edf n\u00ean mong manh \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady?</h2><h2>Khi c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n l\u00fd<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 ho\u00e0ng kim v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2008 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00c1o. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 Tiki-taka tr\u1ee9 danh th\u1ecbnh h\u00e0nh t\u1ea1i La Roja nh\u1edd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Barca Xavi v\u00e0 Iniesta.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean 10 n\u0103m sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3, l\u00fac n\u00e0y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Xavi, trong khi Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng anh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u00f9 v\u1eabn thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ef1 ly nh\u1ecf, song l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7 hay nh\u1eefng pha ch\u1ecdc khe s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Marocco \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng nh\u00e0 vua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Marocco \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng nh\u00e0 vua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Du-am-Tay-Ban-Nha-2-2-Marocco-Dau-roi-bong-dang-nha-vua-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T&nbsp;T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng d\u00f9 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t Morocco \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c do \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tuy nhi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc-421-189558.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/clip-ban-thang-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc-421-189558.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Ma r\u1ed1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\n<span>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Ma r\u1ed1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn l\u00ean t\u1edbi 69%. H\u1ecd tung ra 762 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n so v\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Morocco ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 248, \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c l\u00ean t\u1edbi 91%. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1o n\u00ean l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 16 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u1eadn 11 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch 4. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 hai l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Isco v\u00e0 Iago Aspas, T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Fernando Hierro s\u1ebd c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c danh hi\u1ec7u World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Morocco, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea7u b\u00f2, khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n thua cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> kh\u1edfi tranh, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a La Roja l\u00e0 David De Gea, c\u00e1i t\u00ean v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u v\u00e0 \u0111o\u1ea1t danh hi\u1ec7u &quot;G\u0103ng tay v\u00e0ng&quot; c\u00f9ng MU.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha bao g\u1ed3m: Dani Carvajal, Sergio Ramos, Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Jordi Alba \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1edbi th\u00e2m ni\u00ean ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea3 ch\u1ee5c n\u0103m trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd s\u1edbm t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nam Phi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 8 n\u0103m. Tuy nhi\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1i sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Morocco \u0111\u00eam qua.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Marocco \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng nh\u00e0 vua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Marocco \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng nh\u00e0 vua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/2018-06-25t180655z215267534rc1fde3370d0rtrmadp3soccer-worldcup-esp-mar-15299502061122102997285.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1eeba qua</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 Gerard Pique l\u00e0 hai l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Hierro cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean so v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nam Phi, c\u1eb7p sao hi\u1ebfm hoi c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i sau 8 n\u0103m \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n x\u01b0a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Carvajal v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f2n Jordi Alba kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ecbu t\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n thua \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, cao g\u1ea5p 2,5 so v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua m\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a &lsquo;Ng\u00e0i r\u00e2u k\u1ebdm&rsquo; Vicente del Bosque ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh chinh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2010.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 8 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i sau 537 ph\u00fat h\u1ecd m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd m\u1edf toang c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-hierro-phat-bieu-sau-tran-tbn-22-ma-roc-421-189572.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Morocco</span>, HLV Hiero \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng &quot;n\u1eafn g\u00e2n&quot; c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: &ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. H\u00e3y t\u1ef1 ph\u00ea ph\u00e1n ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 r\u00fat ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc. T\u00f4i tin h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng B, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 TBN \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i v\u1eabn \u0111ang mang t\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 lo \u00e2u. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i HLV ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd G \u0111ang t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi La Roja, khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba thi\u1ebfu g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u1eeba li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1eeda sai tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc-421-189565.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/diem-nhan-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc-421-189565.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau m\u00e0n &ldquo;h\u00fat ch\u1ebft&rdquo; c\u1ee7a TBN tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 phim kinh d\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kaliningrad. \u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ecdng l\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-hierro-phat-bieu-sau-tran-tbn-22-ma-roc-421-189572.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-hierro-phat-bieu-sau-tran-tbn-22-ma-roc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-hierro-phat-bieu-sau-tran-tbn-22-ma-roc-421-189572.html\">HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ea7y lo \u00e2u sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1ecdc Ma R\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nHLV Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn TBN 2-2 Ma R\u1ed1c. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i cho \u00f4ng nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i lo l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc-461-189562.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/1529954926380_lc_galleryImage_KALININGRAD_RUSSIA_JUNE_2.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc-461-189562.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2-2 Mar\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, Mar\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1y h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, l\u00e0m \u00f4ng l\u1edbn TBN ph\u1ea3i tim \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n run b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. Mar\u1ed1c li\u00ean t\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"590","checkdouble":"189595"},{"date":"11:40 26/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 26/6: Ronaldo x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/ngay-hom-nay-266.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (26/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">HLV Carlos Queiroz c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Iran nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng theo lu\u1eadt thi \u0111\u1ea5u, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khu\u1ef7u tay ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/20180625T215355Z_1060178654_RC12CEA975D0_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPIRNPOR.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ea7y c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Cristiano Ronaldo su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 sau khi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng penalty \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iran.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, v\u00e0o ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 83 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha gi\u1eadt c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf v\u1edbi Morteza Pouraliganji. Sau nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Enrique Caceres ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd VAR \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng song cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ch\u1ec9 r\u00fat ra th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Carlos Queiroz c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Iran chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, b\u1edfi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha l\u00e0 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Ch\u1eb3ng sao c\u1ea3 v\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quen \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ph\u1ea3i cho d\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o VAR, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ra \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i b\u1eb1ng khu\u1ef7u tay r\u1ed3i. Theo lu\u1eadt thi \u0111\u1ea5u, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khu\u1ef7u tay \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 Messi hay Ronaldo \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa\", thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Iran kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>B\u00e0i chi ti\u1ebft t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y</em><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bat-luc-hlv-iran-len-tieng-doi-the-do-cho-ronaldo-421-189569.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/queiroz.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bat-luc-hlv-iran-len-tieng-doi-the-do-cho-ronaldo-421-189569.html\">B\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c, HLV Iran l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00f2i th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo</span><br>\r\n<span>Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Iran m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 su\u00fdt n\u1eefa b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n. Sau tr\u1eadn, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Iran \u2013 HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Brazil l\u1ea1i m\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Tin x\u1ea5u \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0110T Brazil khi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng g\u1eb7p Serbia, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Douglas Costa c\u00f3 v\u1ebb s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n do \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp \u0111\u00f9i t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Costa Rica. HLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i t\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-0, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nga cho bi\u1ebft ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Costa n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0 anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 3 tu\u1ea7n, t\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u1ee1 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a World Cup.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 266 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 266 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Tin-nong-World-Cup-2018-hom-nay,-tin-tuc-World-Cup-ngay-266-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Douglas Costa</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p mu\u1ed1n \u201ckh\u00f3a mi\u1ec7ng\u201d HLV \u0110an M\u1ea1ch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">1 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HLV Age Hareide c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o khi cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u201ckh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t\u201d, thi\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 n\u00f3i Paul Pogba ch\u1ec9 lo \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f3c. Nh\u1eefng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi nh\u1edb b\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 HLV Didier Deschamps m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd cho \u0110an M\u1ea1ch m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua nh\u1edb \u0111\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecdc bi\u1ebft nghe. H\u1ecd nh\u1edb r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 \u00f4ng ta \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec. N\u1ebfu \u00f4ng ta mu\u1ed1n th\u00eam m\u1eafm, th\u00eam mu\u1ed1i hay h\u1ea1t ti\u00eau v\u00e0o m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ea9u n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m \u00f4ng ta kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac\u201d, HLV Deschamps kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<h2><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-khi-day-mesut-ozil-len-bang-ghe-du-bi-421-189587.html\" target=\"_blank\">Reus l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Ozil</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb HLV Joachim Low \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Mesut Ozil v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 & \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean. Marco Reus m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cMesut k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eabn ngh\u0129 cho t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\u201d.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 266 Ronaldo x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 266 Ronaldo x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Tin-nong-World-Cup-2018-ngay-266-Ronaldo-xung-dang-nhan-the-do-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Alderweireld kho\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Kane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 & \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng G nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p nhau \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. Trung v\u1ec7 Toby Alderweireld m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y n\u00f3i anh r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB Harry Kane, \u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Harry, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t. Ch\u1eb7n Harry l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ee7 h\u00f2a Ba Lan</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng H khi hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng d\u00f9 c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Senegal, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Makoto Hasebe c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ki\u1ebfm ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i. \u201cNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ea7m c\u1ef1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i\u201d, Hasebe n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"589","checkdouble":"189599"},{"date":"07:40 26/06","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/huyen-thoai-nuoc-anh-chui-boi-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-bo-dao-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Seleccao, \u0110T Iran \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, v\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Alan Shearer ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\r\n</h2><h2><br />\r\nShearer ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch VAR<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eedi th\u1ec1, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch&rdquo; &ndash; Alan Shearer b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Cedric Soares \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau khi theo d\u00f5i b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Shearer cho r\u1eb1ng VAR \u0111ang b\u1ecb l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t anh ch\u00e0ng r\u1ea5t may m\u1eafn, b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu Iran ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t khung c\u1ea3nh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n. Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, t\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao anh ta quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu anh ta nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh quay ch\u1eadm, v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u00edch, anh ta l\u00e0 th\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u00ean. Ch\u1eb3ng l\u1ebd b\u1ea1n th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u00fac n\u00e0o h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1m tay v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng? Cedric Soares kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3. Anh ta c\u00e1ch n\u1eeda met v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm nghi\u1ec1n.&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alan Shearer ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alan Shearer ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/huyen-thoai-nuoc-anh-chui-boi-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-bo-dao-nha.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alan Shearer ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3 15 met v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Ban \u0111\u1ea7u anh ta kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR. Th\u1eadt l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang b\u1ecb l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Didier Drogba chung quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Shearer, r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o VAR. C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi m\u1ebb n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i kh\u00e1c, v\u00e0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm ra h\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Alan Shearer ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 sai, n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o k\u1ef3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc-421-189564.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n</span> trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed (19 l\u1ea7n), d\u00f9 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111i h\u1ebft v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-santos-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-may-man-cua-bo-dao-nha-421-189570.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-santos-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-may-man-cua-bo-dao-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-santos-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-may-man-cua-bo-dao-nha-421-189570.html\">HLV Santos n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha?</span><br />\r\nV\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Fernando Santos chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Iran.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bat-luc-hlv-iran-len-tieng-doi-the-do-cho-ronaldo-421-189569.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/queiroz.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bat-luc-hlv-iran-len-tieng-doi-the-do-cho-ronaldo-421-189569.html\">B\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c, HLV Iran l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00f2i th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo</span><br />\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Iran m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 su\u00fdt n\u1eefa b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n. Sau tr\u1eadn, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Iran &ndash; HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 1-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br />\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Iran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/6.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"588","checkdouble":"189575"},{"date":"07:02 26/06","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (26/6/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2662018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Australia vs Peru trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nAustralia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018, song nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru (21h00 ng\u00e0y 2606) Hy v\u1ecdng mong manh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru (21h00 ng\u00e0y 2606) Hy v\u1ecdng mong manh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nhan-dinh-Australia-vs-Peru-(21h00-ngay-2606)-Hy-vong-mong-manh-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nMile Jedinak v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p r\u1eddi s\u00e2n sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 sau khi b\u1ecb thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u00fat 80 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n Aziz Behich bay v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn Australia nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua 1-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, Australia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7, Christian Eriksen \u0111\u00e3 tung c\u00fa volley ng\u1eabu h\u1ee9ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Mile Jedinak \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1. Trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, Australia t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ngang ng\u1eeda v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng, Mile Jedinak v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7m nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kangaroo kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nAustralia vs Peru trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018. D\u00f9 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Australia vs Peru\" title=\"Preview Australia vs Peru\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Australia-vs-Peru.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Australia vs Peru \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Australia s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kangaroo \u0111ang k\u00e9m &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec&rdquo; 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i Australia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Peru v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch m\u1edbi c\u00f3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nHi\u1ec7n Australia \u0111ang c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 (-1) trong khi \u0111\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 (+1). N\u1ebfu \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1 b\u00e0n, Australia th\u1eafng Peru v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1 b\u00e0n. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m (4) v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 (0).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 2 tr\u1eadn. Mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, Australia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Australia th\u1eafng Peru, c\u00f2n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nWorld Cup 2006, Australia \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c, NHM \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kangaroo s\u1ebd t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 12 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zlatko Kranjcar.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Peru kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Peru v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat, song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mot ngay that vong voi dai dien Nam My khi Phap loai Peru khoi World Cup 2018 bang chien thang toi thieu 1-0.\" title=\"M\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 khi Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i Peru kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/thu-thanh-gallese-khang-dinh-dt-peru-chua-bo-cuoc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Peru \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Australia tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nPeru \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 8 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 6 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Peru c\u00f3 6/8 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ricardo Gareca c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1edbi 27 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 11m nh\u01b0ng Christian Cueva l\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nD\u00f9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m song Peru l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra non n\u1edbt v\u00e0 v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh trong nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTr\u1eadn Australia vs Peru h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Peru s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec danh d\u1ef1. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Australia vs Peru\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Australia vs Peru\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Australia-vs-Peru-(4-4-1-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Australia vs Peru</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 2-1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"587","checkdouble":"189576"},{"date":"07:12 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p (21h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6): C\u00e1i b\u1eaft tay c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c2u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/Dan-Mach-vs-Phap.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018: M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 theo ch\u00e2n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea7u h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u1edf Luzhniki.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Dan Mach vs Phap\" title=\"Preview \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Dan-Mach-vs-Phap.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia v\u00e0 Peru \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p s\u1edbm \u0111o\u1ea1t v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Didier Deschamps \u0111ang ch\u1ecbu s\u1ee9c \u00e9p n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 v\u00ec nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u \u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p (21h00 ng\u00e0y 266) C\u00e1i b\u1eaft tay c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p (21h00 ng\u00e0y 266) C\u00e1i b\u1eaft tay c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Nhan-dinh-Dan-Mach-vs-Phap-(21h00-ngay-266)-Cai-bat-tay-cua-nguoi-Au-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng, c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 20 n\u0103m ch\u01b0a c\u1ea7n m\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u0129 di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 qu\u00ean \u0111i nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n knock-out h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n b\u1ea5t tr\u1eafc mu\u00f4n ph\u1ea7n. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Griezmann, Mbappe, Pogba... c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd hay l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, Les Bleus c\u0169ng s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t lu\u00f4n c\u1ea3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o tay \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 trong v\u00f2ng 1/8, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng g\u00ec cho Ph\u00e1p, khi h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1eaby v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Christian Eriksen Dan Mach\" title=\"Christian Eriksen \u0110an M\u1ea1ch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/christian-eriksen-dan-mach-co-the-dong-vai-phan-dien-khong-phai-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ef1c \u1ed5n khi tr\u1ea3i qua 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u0169 b\u00e3o \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Peru trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. Kasper Schmeichel ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty c\u1ee7a Australia m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t huy s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p. C\u1ea7u h\u00f2a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Ch\u1eb3ng may th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n cho h\u1ecd khi Australia kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1nh th\u1eafng Australia nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Age Hareide kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ph\u00f3 m\u1eb7c v\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tay k\u1ebb kh\u00e1c khi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u1ecd v\u1ed1n to\u00e0n quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch thu\u1ed9c d\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng c\u00f9n th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u h\u00f2a l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 cho \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 n\u00ean ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i b\u1eaft tay h\u00f2a nh\u00e3 gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng s\u00e1nh b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">World Cup 2018 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang hien tai cua bang C World Cup 2018\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/C.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch (4-2-3-1): 1. Schmeichel; 14. Dalsgaard &ndash; 4. Kjaer &ndash; 6. Christensen &ndash; 17. Larsen; 8. Delaney &ndash; 19. Schone; 11. Braithwaite &ndash; 10. Eriksen &ndash; 23. Sisto; 9. Jorgensen<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1p (4-4-2): 16. Mandanda; 19. Sidibe &ndash; 4. Varane &ndash; 3. Kimpembe &ndash; 21. Hernandez; 11. Dembele &ndash; 15. N&rsquo;Zonzi &ndash; 13. Kante &ndash; 8. Lemar; 7. Griezmann &ndash; 9. Giroud<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p: 0-0\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Dan Mach vs Phap\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Dan-Mach-vs-Phap-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-4-2).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"586","checkdouble":"189577"},{"date":"07:12 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina (1h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6): V\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng, v\u1eeba c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/Nigeria-vs-Argentina.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018: Th\u1eafng c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac c\u1ee7a Croatia trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Nigeria vs Argentina\" title=\"Preview Nigeria vs Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Nigeria-vs-Argentina.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Argentina \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9o ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u00f9ng c\u1ef1c.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty h\u1ecfng \u0103n c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i kinh ho\u00e0ng ba b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n m\u00e0 n\u00f3i Argentina kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. \u1ea4y v\u1eady m\u00e0 tr\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea5t v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i cho h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i sau cu\u1ed1i, khi Nigeria b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e1nh g\u1ee5c Iceland \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng D tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1edd th\u00ec ngo\u00e0i Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1eafm cho c\u1ea3 ba c\u00e1i t\u00ean kia, v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh m\u1ed9t Argentina \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ed5 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng Nigeria \u0111\u00eam nay, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi hy v\u1ecdng Iceland kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Croatia s\u1ebd tung ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi xoay quanh th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nghi\u00eam t\u00fac.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi cung DT Argentina\" title=\"Messi cung DT Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/ngay-hom-nay-246.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u01a1 m\u00e0 h\u00e3y khoan b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Argentina v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 khi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i d\u1ec5 nh\u01b0 \u0103n s\u1eb5n cho h\u1ecd. Ch\u00ednh ra m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd ng\u00fat ng\u00e0n v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 n\u1ea3y sinh trong c\u01a1n bi\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n cho hay, HLV Jorge Sampaoli \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 c\u00f2n Sergio Aguero, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb x\u1eed tr\u1ea3m. \u0110o\u00e0n k\u1ebft b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0103n ai, gi\u1edd Argentina s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ra sao v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng r\u1ed1i ren \u0111i\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3o nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y? Li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ngh\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh v\u00e0 l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda si\u00eau h\u1eb9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft m\u00ecnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Nigeria kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c m\u00e0 tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda v\u00f2ng 1/8 h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Argentina khi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a l\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland c\u00e0ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u Phi t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nigeria thap sang co hoi di tiep\" title=\"Nigeria th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Gernot-Rohr-noi-ve-tran-Nigeria-vs-Iceland-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Argentina bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn, bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eabn v\u00f4 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng khi Croatia kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh nh\u1eb1m tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n gi\u00e0nh ba \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Iceland. L\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng d\u00e2ng cao, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u00e1i b\u1eaby ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Nigeria gi\u0103ng ra ch\u1edd s\u1eb5n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; n\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i v\u1eabn thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 con th\u00fa b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra Nigeria kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u1ecfi ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecbu s\u1ee9c \u00e9p kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 m\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb Argentina.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m c\u1ea3 \u1edf Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t khi h\u1ecd g\u1ee1 r\u1ed1i trong c\u1ea3 kh\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1eabn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 hay gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u0169ng quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m. H\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft, Argentina c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 khi c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm r\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i trong s\u1ef1 t\u1ee7i nh\u1ee5c b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m tr\u1eadn Croatia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina 1h00 ng\u00e0y 276 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina 1h00 ng\u00e0y 276 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Nhan-dinh-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-1h00-ngay-276-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nigeria (3-5-2): 23. Uzoho; 6. Balogun &ndash; 5. Troost-Ekong &ndash; 22. Omeruo; 11. Moses &ndash; 4. Ndidi &ndash; 10. Mikel &ndash; 8. Etebo &ndash; 21. Ebuehi; 14. Iheanacho &ndash; 7. Musa<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Argentina (4-3-3): 12. Armani; 18. Salvio &ndash; 2. Mercado &ndash; 17. Otamendi &ndash; 3. Tagliafico; 7. Banega &ndash; 14. Mascherano &ndash; 15. Perez; 10. Messi &ndash; 9. Higuain &ndash; 11. Di Maria<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina: 2-3\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Nigeria vs Argentina\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nigeria vs Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Nigeria-vs-Argentina-(3-5-2-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nigeria vs Argentina</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"585","checkdouble":"189578"},{"date":"07:52 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru (21h00 ng\u00e0y 26/06): C\u00f2n s\u1ed1ng l\u00e0 c\u00f2n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/nhan-dinh-australia-vs-peru-21h00-ngay-2606-con-song-la-con-chien-dau.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Australia vs Peru trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nAustralia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018, song nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru (21h00 ng\u00e0y 2606) Hy v\u1ecdng mong manh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru (21h00 ng\u00e0y 2606) Hy v\u1ecdng mong manh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nhan-dinh-Australia-vs-Peru-(21h00-ngay-2606)-Hy-vong-mong-manh-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nMile Jedinak v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p r\u1eddi s\u00e2n sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 sau khi b\u1ecb thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u00fat 80 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n Aziz Behich bay v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn Australia nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua 1-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, Australia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7, Christian Eriksen \u0111\u00e3 tung c\u00fa volley ng\u1eabu h\u1ee9ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Mile Jedinak \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1. Trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, Australia t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ngang ng\u1eeda v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng, Mile Jedinak v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7m nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kangaroo kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nAustralia vs Peru trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018. D\u00f9 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Australia vs Peru\" title=\"Preview Australia vs Peru\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Australia-vs-Peru.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Australia vs Peru \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Australia s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kangaroo \u0111ang k\u00e9m &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec&rdquo; 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i Australia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Peru v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch m\u1edbi c\u00f3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nHi\u1ec7n Australia \u0111ang c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 (-1) trong khi \u0111\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 (+1). N\u1ebfu \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1 b\u00e0n, Australia th\u1eafng Peru v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1 b\u00e0n. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m (4) v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 (0).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 2 tr\u1eadn. Mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, Australia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Australia th\u1eafng Peru, c\u00f2n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nWorld Cup 2006, Australia \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c, NHM \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kangaroo s\u1ebd t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 12 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zlatko Kranjcar.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Peru kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Peru v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat, song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mot ngay that vong voi dai dien Nam My khi Phap loai Peru khoi World Cup 2018 bang chien thang toi thieu 1-0.\" title=\"M\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 khi Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i Peru kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/thu-thanh-gallese-khang-dinh-dt-peru-chua-bo-cuoc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Peru \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Australia tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nPeru \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 8 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 6 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Peru c\u00f3 6/8 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ricardo Gareca c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1edbi 27 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 11m nh\u01b0ng Christian Cueva l\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nD\u00f9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m song Peru l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra non n\u1edbt v\u00e0 v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh trong nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTr\u1eadn Australia vs Peru h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Peru s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec danh d\u1ef1. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Australia vs Peru\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Australia vs Peru\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Australia-vs-Peru-(4-4-1-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Australia vs Peru</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 2-1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"584","checkdouble":"189579"}]}